OL,3,GNorthern Ireland
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FCloudy with scattered showers.
OL,6,FThese showers become frequent, heavy
OL,7,Fand blustery with hail and thunder at
OL,8,Ftimes from the morning. The strong
OL,9,Fwest to southwest wind will reach gale
OL,10,Fforce in places.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FBlustery showers will clear
OL,13,Ffrom the east during the evening.
OL,14,FIncreasing clear periods and winds
OL,15,Ffalling light bring a patchy inland
OL,16,Ffrost.
OL,17,
OL,18,CMonday:FThe morning will begin mostly
OL,19,Fdry with bright spells. Cloud and
OL,20,Fscattered showers soon spread north.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
