OL,3,GNorthern Ireland
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Tuesday to Thursday:FDry
OL,6,Fwith sunny periods Tuesday morning.
OL,7,FCloud and rain, heavy at times,
OL,8,Fspreads northeast late Tuesday morning
OL,9,Fcontinuing through Tuesday night. This
OL,10,Frain turns showery during Wednesday
OL,11,Fbefore clearing Thursday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
